## Calling a Mutator Method 

#### When we call the method, we pass the **new value** to assign the `age` instance variable. 


<img src="https://images.code.org/1fd6feae0f02e0c8ee592ee50b92ffc2-image-1747931200834.png" alt="code for a mutator method called setName" width="350px" style="border-radius:10px;display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">

